readables/man2/journal_thomas
{
	precache
	"num_pages"	: "2"
	"page1_left_title"	:
	{
		"11 January"
	}
	"page1_left_body"	:
	{
		""
		""
		"This is turning out to be a pretty good job. The pay isn't that great, but the free room and board makes up for it.  "
		""
		"With Lord Twistleton buying up all these properties, I should have lots of work for the forseeable future.  The tenants all seem to be well-to-do folks, and everyone seems to want some sort of secret room installed.  "
		""
		""
	}
	"page1_right_title"	:
	{
		"13 January"
	}
	"page1_right_body"	:
	{
		""
		""
		"Met the rest of the staff here today.  Roland is the cook, although he only works for the Inglebys in flat 3.  We get along pretty well, and he sneaks me leftovers sometimes."
		""
		"Hales is the 'Chief of Security'.  We have no idea what her first name is.  She is strictly business and not terribly friendly.  Roland even tried to bring her some "
	}
	"page2_left_title"	:
	{
		""
	}
	"page2_left_body"	:
	{
		""
		"tarts, but she told him to 'bugger off'."
	}
	"page2_right_title"	:
	{
		""
	}
	"page2_right_body"	:
	{
		""
	}
